[thinking] 
[thinking] It seems like XML4J isolated covers are similar, which is good. I’m thinking about whether I could isolate a direct active test without using ServiceLoader by directly instantiating IsolatedXercesDomAdapterCallable, but that might not really isolate it. The ServiceLoader seems like the only way to load the callable class through a child. An alternative could be using ClassLoader.loadClass and then asSubclass, but that feels a bit reflective and unsupported. I guess existing setups are okay. No tests are needed, though I could consider using grep and maybe a git diff.
